To make a product safety inquiry with Oxford University Press, you can use the general contact options provided on the Oxford Learner's Dictionaries website:

1. **Email**: Send your inquiry to the support address **eltdict.help@oup.com**. In the email, clearly state that your request concerns a product safety issue and include any relevant product details.
